name: Furisode Girl Kirika (Pokemon XY)
description:
Furisode Girl Kirika from pokemon x and pokemon y

Use furisode_kirika as trigger word.

Trained on Nai

You may want to add "detached sleeves", to your Prompt


Can be used at 1.0 weight but you should lower it if you want to change her clothes

Most of my traning data she had her arms up, so it tends to generate like that, to avoid you can try to specify using something like "hands on hip" in your prompt and you can also try adding "arms up" and "arm up" in your negative prompt

All images were generated using yabalMix (https://civitai.com/models/28648/yabalmix) with xformers on and using kl-f8-anime2 vae.

images were generated at 512x768 and upscaled using highres fix by 1.95 and using 4x_foolhardy_Remacri upscaler
